    "cff_info": "<div id=\"fieldInfoBrainMetastases\" style=\" margin-top: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px;\">\n  <h4>Brain Metastases Epilepsy Risk Score</h4>\n  <p><i>Wolpert et al., 2020</i></p>\n  <p><b>DOI:</b> <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1093/neuonc/noz172\" target=\"_blank\">10.1093/neuonc/noz172</a></p>\n  <h4>Factors and Points</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li><b>Supratentorial Brain Metastases (BM):</b> 4 points</li>\n    <li><b>Incomplete Resection:</b> 3 points</li>\n    <li><b>Multiple Surgeries:</b> 1 point</li>\n  </ul>\n  <h4>Risk Estimates</h4>\n  <p>Predicted risk of epilepsy after 5 years based on the score:</p>\n  <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: #f2f2f2;\">\n        <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Score</th>\n        <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Risk</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">0 points</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">0%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">1 point</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">0%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">2 points</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">No data</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">3 points</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">6.3%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">4 points</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">8.7%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">5 points</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">11.1%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">6 points</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">No data</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">7 points</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">22.9%</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">8 points</td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">47.4%</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <h4>Additional Study Information</h4>\n  <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px;\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr style=\"background-color: #f2f2f2;\">\n        <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Category</th>\n        <th style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Details</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Population</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Derivation: 799 patients, Zurich (2004-2014).</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Statistical Methods</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Univariate and multivariate Cox regression models.</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Performance Metrics</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">AUC: 0.75 (derivation).</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Generalizability</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Moderate (limited by retrospective design).</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\"><b>Clinical Utility</b></td>\n        <td style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 8px;\">Helps identify high-risk patients for anti-seizure medication (ASM) treatment or potential prophylaxis.</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>",
